16:09.760 --> 16:11.260
I've killed men for less!

16:11.262 --> 16:13.028
Murder's my favorite!

16:13.030 --> 16:15.164
Oh! Oh!

16:15.166 --> 16:16.665
Damn it!

16:16.667 --> 16:18.834
