17:14.892 --> 17:16.290
- Puffy?
- Very puffy.

17:16.292 --> 17:19.428
And-- and thinly lipped,

17:19.430 --> 17:21.696
like-- like carpaccio.

17:21.699 --> 17:23.598
Yeah, yeah.

17:23.601 --> 17:28.637
It kind of resembles
the coastline of New Hampshire.

17:28.639 --> 17:30.439
Well, is that true?

17:30.441 --> 17:32.407
Is that what your vagina
looks like?

17:32.409 --> 17:34.810
Well, I don't know
what my vagina looks like.

17:34.812 --> 17:36.411
I've never seen it.

17:36.413 --> 17:37.579
Oh!

17:37.581 --> 17:39.414
