17:39.416 --> 17:41.483
That's because we butcher pigs.

17:41.485 --> 17:45.254
And I've seen a dog's vagina
before...

17:45.256 --> 17:47.689
Just on the street.

17:47.691 --> 17:50.392
Well, there's only one way
to solve this mystery.

17:50.394 --> 17:51.660
Show us.

17:51.662 --> 17:53.028
I'll show mine.

17:53.030 --> 17:54.429
It's tight
and smells of chutney.

17:54.431 --> 17:55.931
Lillian, have some dignity.

17:55.933 --> 17:57.599
This is a court of law.

17:58.669 --> 17:59.968
Ma'am, please stand up

17:59.970 --> 18:02.070
