18:04.808 --> 18:07.776
If it pleases the court.

18:07.778 --> 18:09.645
That remains to be seen.

18:27.531 --> 18:31.667
I give you the coastline
of New Hampshire!

18:34.004 --> 18:35.837
New Hampshire!

18:35.839 --> 18:38.707
Seems our problem
has been solved.

18:38.709 --> 18:40.742
What?
No! No, no, no.

18:40.744 --> 18:42.244
You can't decide a trial

18:42.246 --> 18:44.146
